{"tid":2018932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人法國連登仔行動力近日廢左唔少","createTime":"2020-05-16T02:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T03:22:17.000Z","uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf463906a32f88326b8b7f5775f4198fa48c1c6f","tid":2018932,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:38:54.000Z","msg":"簽個泰國聯署都簽唔成<br />\n<br />\n以前逢親有行動都有巴打周圍貼行動資訊<br />\n我仲記得#2有六四青年叫人去維園，同埋有架飛機撞埋黎叫人去和你飛嘅3D圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家啲行動概念得個up字<br />\n大家傾咁做咁做幾好呀，傾左幾十頁有幾千正評<br />\n但冇人真正號召搞<br />\n最後就不了了之<br />\n<br />\n有時出面號召活動<br />\n連登都冇人提<br />\n要直播開始先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢連登連資訊版功能都廢撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為市民大眾都好嬲好嬲<br />\n而家群眾其實慢慢累積緊行動力<br />\n淨係計連登，攬炒巴個post都有萬幾正評，仲未計CD rom，呢啲人應該係call得郁<br />\n<br />\n我見組愛國團隊示威<br />\n同527行動個post都有好多idea，由邊度開始集合之類<br />\n希望我地討論完真係會有結論會call行動<br />\n咁樣先會有源源不絕嘅新抗爭方式<br />\n<br />\n唔好話咩俾狗知部署點搞<br />\n你要人多嘅活動就冇計<br />\n一係閉門做車，搞壇野得十幾人做<br />\n但我覺得大堆頭行動同小隊行動兩者都應該繼續搞<br />\n而大堆行動應該係借力打力式行動為佳，係預左俾狗知嘅行動<br />\n<br />\n唔好話咩搞活動都係靠tg<br />\n冇足夠嘅討論出面啲搞手嘅行動好易變得因循<br />\n見一樣野work就不斷搞落去搞到爛為止<br />\n連登好處係一個idea 可能有幾千人討論幾千人正評<br />\n集思廣益效用好大<br />\n係差臨門號召一腳<br />\n<br />\n而家我地全方位被打擊<br />\n創意好重要<br />\n和你sing爛之前我地應該已經要prepare 定其他抗爭策略<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8020270e89191af4decef7a43fcd866896a54699","tid":2018932,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702b71853d3da9dfbe2bcad9d7885802c42f7b86","tid":2018932,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b690b3953077e0c55694f481a149575387d02b9","tid":2018932,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:40:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔話你知新登係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"13cc716bbba332731793fae3085474d4ef549fa7","tid":2018932,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f0161d21af5571fbafc92134236d9a2b477fa2","tid":2018932,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1b6d334817d83d0068865041244c919b68e591","tid":2018932,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"連登已經俾cctai班友玩爛咗"},{"pid":"4d57203e743020619deb169fe630b2b3ce1c2b0d","tid":2018932,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T03:22:17.000Z","msg":"運動勝左 反送中都撤回左 咁仲出黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face